Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.80,0:00:09.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.90,0:00:13.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,塔茲米 我們差不多該走了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.39,0:00:17.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們走這邊 塔茲米回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.00,0:00:21.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說什麼啊 我們三個一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.21,0:00:24.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是已經有新的小夥伴了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.22,0:00:26.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可不能總是向我們撒嬌哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.75,0:00:29.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再見了 塔茲米
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.84,0:00:32.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果有來世的話 在那裡再見吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.88,0:00:35.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.12,0:00:38.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要把我一個人…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.33,0:00:54.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是難忘的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.11,0:00:59.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然睡在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.12,0:01:06.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說從今天開始塔茲米就是我的部下了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.90,0:01:08.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.40,0:01:10.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天然呆上司出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.67,0:01:20.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.93,0:01:27.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 眼鏡眼鏡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.63,0:01:33.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.01,0:03:17.82,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,赤瞳作
